  "texts": [
    "The performance of the RAG-augmented Llama was compared against the baseline and other models based on the evaluation metrics described in the experimental setup.",
    "This comparative analysis provided insights into the effectiveness of the reverse proxystyle RAG mechanism in enhancing the factual accuracy and coherence of the generated responses.",
    "ResultsThe results of the experiments demonstrated that the RAGaugmented Llama significantly outperformed the baseline and comparison models in terms of factual accuracy and coherence.",
    "The precision, recall, and F1-score metrics indicated a marked improvement in the accuracy of the responses generated by the RAG-augmented Llama compared to the unaugmented version.",
    "ModelPrecision In addition to accuracy metrics, the coherence of the generated responses was evaluated using BLEU and ROUGE scores."
